pageContext.claim: “Because if you know almost every race that I campaigned for somebody they won. But I couldn't devote too much time to the House, there's too many people. But if you look at some of the Congressmen that I did go for and went for, they won like in Kentucky, et cetera, et cetera.”
pageContext.analysis: An analysis from the Brookings Institution found Trump 64 percent of the candidates that Trump campaigned for won their House or Senate race in 2018.
